
<%- include("../partials/top") %>
<body id="home">
	
	<%- include("../partials/header") %>
	
	<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
		<ol class="carousel-indicators">
			<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
			<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
			<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
		</ol>
		
		<div class="carousel-inner">
			<div class="carousel-item active">
				<img src="/images/slide1.jpg" width="100%" height="100%" 
					 background="#777" color="#777">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="carousel-caption text-left">
						<h1>BOOKWIZARD</h1>
						<p>WE DON’T SIMPLY READ BOOKS. WE BECOME THEM</p>
						<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/register" 
							  role="button">SUBSCRIBE</a>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="carousel-item">
				<img src="/images/slide2.jpg" width="100%" height="100%" background="#777" 
					 color="#777">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="carousel-caption">
						<h1>WANT TO CREATE SOMETHING OF YOUR OWN?</h1>
						<p>Bookwizard offers a great platform for your creations with built-in analysis that allows you to see what your audience is interested in. Now, what are you waiting for?</p>
						<p>
							<a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/blogs" role="button">
								Start Bloging
							</a>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="carousel-item">
				<img src="/images/slide3.jpg" width="100%" height="100%" background="#777" 
					 color="#777">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="carousel-caption text-right">
						<h1>LATEST EVENTS</h1>
						<p>Bookwizard provides you with timely updates about the events and book launches happening around the city that you might be interested in and with necessary information regarding the passes for the event.</p>
						<p>
							<a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/events" role="button">
								View Events
							</a>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
			<span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
			<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
		</a>
		<a class="carousel-control-next" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
			<span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
			<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
		</a>
	</div>
	
	<div class="container marketing">
		<% if(books && books.length > 0){ %>
		<h1 align="center ">Best Seller of the Year</h1><br>
		<div class="row">
			<% books.forEach(function(books){ %>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<img src="<%= books.image %>" width="140" background="#777" color="#777" >
				<h3><%= books.title %></h3>
				<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/books/<%=books._id%>" role="button">
					View details &raquo;</a>
				</p>
			</div>
			<% }) %>
		</div>
		<% } %>
		
		<hr class="featurette-divider">
		
		<div class="row featurette">
			<div class="col-md-7">
				<h2 class="featurette-heading">
					We have an extensive collection of best sellers from different genres,
					<span class="text-muted"> that you can’t miss out on.</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					We offer an appealing selection of quality second-hand and brand new books. Our selection is vast and our prices are unbeatable. No matter your style and taste, we have something for you! Our quality inventory is changing constantly. Whether you’re into following the latest trends or want to start your own, we’ve got what you’re looking for — and at great prices.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5 my-auto">
				<img src="/images/feature1.jpg" width="500" height="500" background="#eee" 
					 color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid my-auto">
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<hr class="featurette-divider">
		
		<div class="row featurette">
			<div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
				<h2 class="featurette-heading">
					Love to Read Ebook?
					<span class="text-muted">We've got you that for free</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					We offer an appealing and vast selection of E-books of different styles and tastes. No matter what your taste is, we’ve something in our store for you. With the ever-increasing popularity of technological dependence, E-books are often considered as the future of literature, albeit nothing can be predicted about the paperbacks as it’s a tradition and history. Bookwizard takes care of the needs of every reader, that’s why we’re offering an extensive collection of E-books for free.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5 order-md-1 my-auto" >
				<img src="/images/feature2.jpg" width="500" height="500" background="#eee" 
					 color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid my-auto">
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<hr class="featurette-divider">
		
		<div class="row featurette">
			<div class="col-md-7">
				<h2 class="featurette-heading">WHO ARE WE<span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
				<p class="lead">
					We Are Bookwizard- The magic wand in the hands of bibliophiles. We offer an extensive collection of books from different genres. We regularly accept donations, consignments and on-spot sales on a regular basis, and our ever-expanding inventory reflects this. Our shoppers benefit from our low prices. Exchange books with other readers of your interest. Bookwizard always looks to promote budding writers with adequate support from eminent authors. Those who sell to us on consignment basis are also satisfied with their profitable returns. Our experienced sales associates helpfully assist shoppers as well as all donation and consignment transactions. Contact us to start shopping or selling today!
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="col-md-5 my-auto">
				<img src="/images/feature3.jpg" width="500" height="500" background="#eee" 
					 color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid my-auto">
			</div>
		</div>
	
	</div>
	
	<%- include("../partials/footer") %>

